xyz.thepathfinder.android

Interface TransportListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Listener<Transport>

    public interface TransportListener
extends Listener<Transport>
    The TransportListener interface gives developers access to notifications when a transport is modified. The notifications also include route notifications.
